The Frontier Enabling Test<br>
The Space Frontier Foundation has devised the &quot;Frontier Enabling Test&quot; to determine whether the Foundation will support or oppose an issue. <br>
<br>
The Frontier Enabling Test defines a frontier enabling technology as one that: <br>
<br>
*        accelerates the creation of low cost access to the space frontier for private citizens and companies; <br>
*        enables or accelerates our use of local space resources; and/or <br>
*        accelerates the rate at which wealth can be generated in space.<br>
<br>
See also their &quot;<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.space-frontier.org/POLICIES/Manifesto.html">Manifesto for the Frontier</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->&quot;.  Important stuff.<br>
