t nuclear power is vital. Our aim has always been the promotion of nuclear power for space. Certainly we can broaden our content. As a space organisation we would be remiss to exclude anything space related. Lets not lose our objective and become just another space group. Nasa is now nuclear and that means most future missions will be incorporating nuclear power in some fashion. The public wont fail to notice this and our news page is going to be flooded with nuclearspace items.<br>
Nuclear is a narrow topic by itself but just as we have categories devoted solely to aaspects of nuclear power we can also have categories devoted solely to space, astronomy, missions etc.    <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
